leri", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5378, "text": "Birisi, y\u00fcksek derecelere sahip olan Allah kat\u0131ndan, inkarc\u0131lara gelecek ve savunulmas\u0131 imkans\u0131z olacak azab\u0131 soruyor."}, {"id": 566430, "identifier": "tr.diyanet", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 568, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 227, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet \u0130\u015fleri", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Isleri", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5379, "text": "Melekler ve Cebrail o derecelere, miktar\u0131 elli bin y\u0131l olan bir g\u00fcnde y\u00fckselirler."}, {"id": 566431, "identifier": "tr.diyanet", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 568, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 227, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet \u0130\u015fleri", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Isleri", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5380, "text": "G\u00fczel g\u00fczel sabret;"}, {"id": 566432, "identifier": "tr.diyanet", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 568, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 227, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet \u0130\u015fleri", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Isleri", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5381, "text": "Do\u011frusu inkarc\u0131lar azab\u0131 uzak g\u00f6r\u00fcyorlar."}, {"id": 566433, "identifier": "tr.diyanet", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 568, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 227, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet \u0130\u015fleri", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Isleri", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5382, "text": "Ama biz onu yak\u0131n g\u00f6rmekteyiz."}, {"id": 566434, "identifier": "tr.diyanet", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 568, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 227, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet \u0130\u015fleri", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Isleri", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5383, "text": "G\u00f6k, o g\u00fcn, erimi\u015f maden gibi olur."}, {"id": 566435, "identifier": "tr.diyanet", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 568, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 227, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet \u0130\u015fleri", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Isleri", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5384, "text": "Da\u011flar da at\u0131lm\u0131\u015f pamu\u011fa d\u00f6ner."}, {"id": 566436, "identifier": "tr.diyanet", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 568, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 227, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet \u0130\u015fleri", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Isleri", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5385, "text": "Hi\u00e7 bir dost di\u011fer bir dostunu sormaz."}, {"id": 566437, "identifier": "tr.diyanet", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 227, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet \u0130\u015fleri", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Isleri", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5386, "text": "Onlar birbirlerine yaln\u0131z g\u00f6sterilirler. Su\u00e7lu kimse o g\u00fcn\u00fcn azab\u0131ndan kurtulmak i\u00e7in o\u011fullar\u0131n\u0131, ailesini, karde\u015fini, kendisini bar\u0131nd\u0131rm\u0131\u015f olan s\u00fclalesini ve yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde bulunan herkesi feda etmek ve b\u00f6ylece kendisini kurtarmak ister."}, {"id": 566438, "identifier": "tr.diyanet", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manz