130\u015fleri", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Isleri", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5416, "text": "Do\u011fular\u0131n ve bat\u0131lar\u0131n Rabbine yemin ederim ki, onlar\u0131n yerine daha iyilerini getirme\u011fe Bizim g\u00fcc\u00fcm\u00fcz yeter ve kimse de \u00f6n\u00fcm\u00fcze ge\u00e7emez."}, {"id": 566470, "identifier": "tr.diyanet", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet \u0130\u015fleri", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Isleri", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5417, "text": "Onlar\u0131 b\u0131rak; kendilerine s\u00f6z verilen g\u00fcne kavu\u015fmalar\u0131na kadar dal\u0131p oynas\u0131nlar."}, {"id": 566471, "identifier": "tr.diyanet", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet \u0130\u015fleri", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Isleri", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5418, "text": "Kabirlerden \u00e7abuk \u00e7abuk \u00e7\u0131kacaklar\u0131 g\u00fcn, g\u00f6zleri d\u00f6nm\u00fc\u015f, y\u00fczlerini zillet b\u00fcr\u00fcm\u00fc\u015f olarak sanki dikili ta\u015flara do\u011fru ko\u015farlar. \u0130\u015fte bu, onlara s\u00f6z verilmi\u015f olan g\u00fcnd\u00fcr."}, {"id": 566472, "identifier": "tr.diyanet", "surah_number": 70, "surah_